OL,4,Csaid he 'didn't deliberately stab'
OL,5,Canyone
OL,7,FThe man accused of murdering a rugby
OL,8,Fplayer outside a nightclub in Bodmin
OL,9,Fhas told a jury he was in "defence
OL,10,Fmode" and "didn't deliberately strike
OL,11,Fanybody" with the knife he was holding.
OL,13,FJake Hill and his co-accused Chelsea
OL,14,FPowell have been charged with the
OL,15,Fmurder of Michael Riddiough-Allen who
OL,16,Fwas stabbed to death outside the
OL,17,FEclipse Nightclub in Bodmin in the
OL,18,Fearly hours of 30 April 2023. Hill is
OL,19,Falso faces other charges in regards to
OL,20,Ffive other victims.
