OL,3,CMan accused of murdering rugby player
OL,4,Csaid he 'didn't deliberately stab'
OL,5,Canyone
OL,7,FOn the third day and final day of
OL,8,Fgiving evidence, Mr Hill explained he
OL,9,Fwas waving the combat knife because he
OL,10,Fhad been knocked to the ground after
OL,11,Fbeing attacked and was unable to get
OL,12,Fup.
OL,14,F"It was in my hand but I didn't
OL,15,Fdeliberately stab it towards anyone",
OL,16,Fhe told Truro Crown Court.
OL,18,F"I was panicking so I was not aware of
OL,19,Fthe knife making contact with anyone."
