OL,5,Canyone
OL,7,FMr Hill said he did not realise people
OL,8,Fhad been stabbed until his friend
OL,9,FRhiannon Tompsett came up to him and
OL,10,Fsaid, "you stabbed me".
OL,12,FHe told the jury that at the time, he
OL,13,Fdid not realise anyone had died that
OL,14,Fnight and found out about Michael
OL,15,FRiddiough-Allen's death on Facebook
OL,16,Flater that morning.
OL,18,FDuring cross examination the
OL,19,Fprosecution accused Mr Hill of lying
OL,20,Fabout the "gaps" in his memories,
OL,21,Fsomething which he denies.
