OL,4,Csaid he 'didn't deliberately stab'
OL,5,Canyone
OL,7,FProsecution barrister Mark Cotter KC
OL,8,Fsaid: "I am going to suggest that that
OL,9,Fis a lie.
OL,11,F"It is impossible to explain those
OL,12,Fevents by your recollection and the
OL,13,Fonly choice you have is to say my
OL,14,Fmemory cuts out."
OL,16,FIn further questioning, Mr Hill
OL,17,Fexplained that he had tried to flush
OL,18,Fthe knife down the toilet and hide it
OL,19,Fin an extractor fan because he was
OL,20,F"scared of getting arrested".
