OL,4,Csaid he 'didn't deliberately stab'
OL,5,Canyone
OL,7,FHe said his mind was going "100 miles
OL,8,Fa minute" and he "panicked" when he
OL,9,Fknew the police were outside the
OL,10,Fproperty.
OL,12,FIn his first police interview after
OL,13,Fbeing arrested, Mr Hill admitted he
OL,14,Fhad lied to officers about being in
OL,15,Fpossession of a knife.
OL,17,FHe said he did this because he thought
OL,18,Fit would damage his version of events
OL,19,Fwhere he was defending himself.
