OL,3,CMan accused of murdering rugby player
OL,4,Csaid he 'didn't deliberately stab'
OL,5,Canyone
OL,7,F"I lied because I didn't think anyone
OL,8,Fwould believe me for one. I was in
OL,9,Fdenial I didn't want to accept someone
OL,10,Fhad died", he told the court.
OL,12,FHe told the jury how he changed his
OL,13,Fstatement to police in his second
OL,14,Finterview, admitting he had a knife
OL,15,Fbecause he had "come to (his) senses
OL,16,Fat that point".
OL,18,FMr Hill denies all the counts against
OL,19,Fhim.
OL,21,FThe trial continues.
